    "body" : "<p>Use this </p>\n\n<pre><code>long startTime = System.currentTimeMillis();\nlong elapsedTime = 0L.\n\nwhile (elapsedTime &lt; 2*60*1000) {\n    //perform db poll/check\n    elapsedTime = (new Date()).getTime() - startTime;\n}\n\n//Throw your exception\n</code></pre>\n"
